msgstr "选择 Elementor 表单如何与 Google Sheets 进行身份验证。"

msgid "Google Account Connection"
msgstr "Google 账户连接"

msgid ""
"Sign in with your Google account to connect Elementor Forms with Google Sheets. "
"Once connected, your data syncs based on your settings. Learn more in the "
"documentation"
msgstr ""
"使用您的 Google 账户登录，以将 Elementor 表单与 Google Sheets 连接。一旦连接，您的"
"数据将根据您的设置进行同步。有关更多信息，请参阅文档"

msgid ""
"<p class=\"fw-400 text-dark\"><strong>Google Drive</strong> and <strong>Google "
"Sheets</strong> permissions were not granted during authentication with Google.</"
"p>\n"
"                                        <p class=\"fw-400 text-"
"dark\"><strong>Refer to Step 4 in the Connection Guide shown alongside.</"
"strong><br> Then, deactivate the connection and re-authorize it, ensuring both "
"Google Drive and Google Sheets permissions are enabled.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p class=\"fw-400 text-dark\"><strong>Google Drive</strong> 和 <strong>Google "
"Sheets</strong> 权限在与 Google 进行身份验证时未被授予。</p>\n"
"                                        <p class=\"fw-400 text-dark\"><strong>请参"
"考旁边的连接指南第 4 步。</strong><br> 然后，停用连接并重新授权，确保启用 Google "
"Drive 和 Google Sheets 权限。</p>"

msgid ""
"Something wrong ! Your Auth Code may be wrong or expired. Please deactivate and "
"do Re-Authentication again. "
msgstr "出现问题！您的授权代码可能错误或已过期。请停用并重新进行身份验证。"

msgid "Save Client Token"
msgstr "保存客户端令牌"

msgid ""
"Connect Elementor Forms to Google Sheets using your own Google Cloud project.\n"
"                            Ideal for advanced users who need full API control, "
"custom OAuth setup,\n"
"                            and independent credential management."
msgstr ""
"使用您自己的 Google Cloud 项目将 Elementor 表单连接到 Google Sheets。\n"
"                            适合需要完全 API 控制、自定义 OAuth 设置和独立凭据管理"
"的高级用户。"

msgid ""
"Securely connect Elementor Forms to Google Sheets using a Google Cloud Service "
